data.description: This well maintained 4 bed, 2 bath home was redefined in 2017 with a fully remodeled kitchen with granite countertops, a huge island with tons of extra counterspace, storage and electricity, Stainless steel appliances, separate pantry and a breakfast bar. An open concept with a split floorplan featuring wood look porcelain tile throughout the main living areas makes this a perfect home designed for entertaining indoors and out! Enjoy the covered patio or spacious backyard while sitting around the fire pit with friends and family!  Impact windows installed in 2021 make for hassle free hurricane preparations and offer added energy efficiency and quiet. The primary suite boasts a huge walk in closet with custom built in shelving and a fully remodeled bathroom that includes double sinks, a separate tub, water closet and shower with added wall jets.  Roof 2019, Tankless Water Heater 2023. Located minutes from neighborhood parks, shopping, dining and I-95. Your future home awaits!
